Sr. Project Manager
06 May 2014 01:19 AM - Qatar
. Job Location: Abu Dhabi
Job Title: Sr. Project Manager
Brief Job Description:
1. Liaise With consultant & Client and streamline the management process
2. Fully in charge of major aspects of the project in terms of safety, technical, material submission, qualify etc, and requested to provide support to Chief Representative /Project Director for contractual matters
3. Manage & Control subcontractors/suppliers to make sure progress & quality to be in line with the project plan
The successful candidate must meet the below criteria:
Must have working experience with contractor
B.Sc or M.Sc in Civil Engineering
Min. 20 yrs post graduate experience
Experience in Bridges, Roads & Tunnels structures.
Managed projects in excess of 300 million( (more...)
